des: Enjoy the Beat Navy spirit of Alexa - Just say, "Alexa, start Go Army" and you'll hear her first of many favorite facts about Navy. Recommended for Naval Academy grads to install so they can learn the truth and eventually switch over to the proper side of discipline and victory. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit once you've reached an acceptable level of Beat Navy spirit. Go Army, Beat Navy.
